    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你的朋友失踪了，一股黑暗势力正在这个已经疯狂的世界中悄然崛起。你，蟾蜍警长，是这个紧张刺激的侧滚轮冒险游戏中唯一能拯救他的蟾蜍！你可以四处跳跃、射击，调查神秘的失踪事件，同时探索这片土地，结识这个宇宙中引人入胜的角色！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/27d1f3ac14e60d019b3e4a5db0b15873.poster.avif?t=1748894741\" width=542 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/27d1f3ac14e60d019b3e4a5db0b15873.webm?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/27d1f3ac14e60d019b3e4a5db0b15873.mp4?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >避开陷阱和危险，以精确的动作在环境中移动，通过沿途的所有障碍！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四处冲刺、爬墙、跳跃，通过这个世界提供的所有挑战！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在海滩、森林、秘密工厂等地漫游，寻找你的朋友。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/dc59fc38ba5d307eb7750ee405321709.poster.avif?t=1748894741\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/dc59fc38ba5d307eb7750ee405321709.webm?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/dc59fc38ba5d307eb7750ee405321709.mp4?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打败沿途的敌人！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用多种武器和特殊能力，以最佳策略应对遭遇战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/12dd0590265a83262a5da4c254afbf55.poster.avif?t=1748894741\" width=542 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/12dd0590265a83262a5da4c254afbf55.webm?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/12dd0590265a83262a5da4c254afbf55.mp4?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的老朋友们已经腐化，想要打败你！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在史诗般的战斗中挑战它们，让它们摆脱疾病！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许以后还能和他们和好？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/d82bbe7d0159775dcb88a0a8528fd00a.webp?t=1748894741\" width=600 height=61 /></span></p>",
